Table of Contents

Namespace NeonSuit.RSSReader.Core.Models.Events

Classes

ArticleTaggedEventArgs

Event arguments for the OnArticleTagged event. Carries data related to an article being tagged, including the article and tag details, who applied the tag, and optional information about the rule and confidence.

ArticleUntaggedEventArgs

Event arguments for the OnArticleUntagged event. Carries data related to a tag being removed from an article.

CleanupCompletedEventArgs

Provides data for the OnCleanupCompleted event. Contains the final results of the cleanup operation.

CleanupProgressEventArgs

Provides data for the OnCleanupProgress event. Reports progress updates during a cleanup operation.

CleanupStartingEventArgs

Provides data for the OnCleanupStarting event. Contains configuration and timing information about the cleanup operation that is about to begin.

PreferenceChangedEventArgs

Event arguments for preference change notifications. Provides data about which preference was modified and its new value.

TagChangedEventArgs

Event arguments for tag change notifications.
